69
00:02:49,402 --> 00:02:52,204
As a father,
it's got to be pretty tough.

70
00:02:52,205 --> 00:02:55,408
The look in her face,
just the sheer terror,

71
00:02:55,443 --> 00:02:57,828
it's painful
