control.

77
00:03:11,891 --> 00:03:14,659
- Now, I understand you're an
ordained minister. - Yes, I am, yeah.

78
00:03:14,694 --> 00:03:17,662
I've done numerous blessings,
and it just doesn't stop.

79
00:03:17,663 --> 00:03:20,366
What are you hoping
we can do for you guys?

80
00:03:20,401 --> 00:03:22,486
We've gone as far as we can
on our own,

81
00:03:22,521 --> 00:03:24,571
and we can't live like this
any longer.

82
00:03:40,619 --> 00:03:43,756
AMY: As usual,
I had absolutely no information

83
00:03:43,791 --> 00:03:46,524
