that the house was overflowing

85
00:03:49,061 --> 00:03:51,530
with dangerous activity,
and just like the living people

86
00:03:51,565 --> 00:03:54,800
that Steve meets,
sometimes the dead I encounter

87
00:03:54,835 --> 00:03:56,601
